          </p>
          <p>
            For Santa Monica specifically, coastal climate accelerates wear on some components —
            which means some appliances here age faster than the national averages suggest. Our
            technicians factor that in when they give you a recommendation. If the same part
            is likely to fail again in 18 months because of where you live, we'll tell you that
            rather than take your money.
